name: Lets-go-fingerboarding
tagline: FingerBoarding is a type of sport followed in most of the countries around the world. But in Nepal this is a new genre of sport and "Lets-go-fingerboarding" is a simple android application that introduces the sport.
body: Hello there!!!! Lets get going and have fun with fingerboarding!!!
